<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">م د ح:</span> <span class="c2">(الْمَدْحُ)</span> الثَّنَاءُ الْحَسَنُ وَبَابُهُ قَطَعَ. وَكَذَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٩٢⦘ <span class="c2">(الْمِدْحَةُ)</span> بِكَسْرِ الْمِيمِ وَ <span class="c2">(الْمَدِيحُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(الْأُمْدُوحَةُ)</span> بِضَمِّ الْهَمْزَةِ. وَ <span class="c2">(امْتَدَحَهُ)</span> مِثْلُ <span class="c2">(مَدَحَهُ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(تَمَدَّحَ)</span> الرَّجُلُ تَكَلَّفَ أَنْ يُمْدَحَ. وَرَجُلٌ <span class="c2">(مُمَدَّحٌ)</span> بِوَزْنِ مُحَمَّدٍ أَيْ <span class="c2">(مَمْدُوحٌ)</span> جِدًّا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>